nodes.text: Seh-Tizle was a female Human who lived during the Cold War between the Galactic Republic and the Sith Empire. She worked in the Olaris spaceport's mess hall in the bombed and destroyed city world of Taris.
Seh-Tizle first appeared in Star Wars: The Old Republic, a video game released by BioWare in 2011, as a cantina vendor in the Olaris Mess Hall on Taris.
